<title>SOUTH AFRICA: GF Coal declares interim div, cap award.</title>
<headline>GF Coal declares interim div, cap award.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-06-11</dateline>
<text>
<p>Type of share: ordinary</p>
<p>Period: six months ended June 30</p>
<p>Interim div 60 cts</p>
<p>Pay date: after July 4</p>
<p>Record date: June 27</p>
<p>Full name: Gold Fields Coal Ltd</p>
<p>NOTE - Directors said they would make a capitalisation share award, details of which would be published around June 23.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
</text>
